<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <title>Payment Success Lightbox</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f0f0;
        }

        .resultbox {
            display: flex;
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .resultbox_content {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            width: 500px;
            height: 300px;
        }

        .resultbox_content svg {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            margin: 0px 10px;
        }

        .resultbox_content p {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #242424;
        }

        .resultbox_content p1 {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #6c6c6c;
        }

        .resultbox_content button {
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        .resultbox_content button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        .btn-success__link {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="resultbox" id="page_resultbox">
        <div class="resultbox_content">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512">
                <!--!Font Awesome Free 6.6.0 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free Copyright 2024 Fonticons, Inc.-->
                <path fill="#5fe704"
                    d="M256 512A256 256 0 1 0 256 0a256 256 0 1 0 0 512zM369 209L241 337c-9.4 9.4-24.6 9.4-33.9 0l-64-64c-9.4-9.4-9.4-24.6 0-33.9s24.6-9.4 33.9 0l47 47L335 175c9.4-9.4 24.6-9.4 33.9 0s9.4 24.6 0 33.9z" />
            </svg>
            <p>Thanh toán thành công</p>
            <p1>
                Cảm ơn bạn đã thanh toán. Chúng tôi sẽ liên hệ để biết thêm chi tiết
                trong thời gian ngắn!
            </p1>
            <button class="btn-success"><a class="btn-success__link" href="/">
                    Trở về
                </a>
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>